  "thirdPartyHooks": [
    {
      "_comment": "useDialogContext comes from @kobalte/core/dialog. It requires a <Kobalte> ancestor in the same JSX tree, not a Solid Provider mount. Out of scope for this registry — Kobalte handles its own propagation. Phase-10-Audit flagged a latent propagation issue via Kobalte.Portal (see _audit/Phase-10-Provider-Matrix-2026-06-27.md).",
